{"tid":919034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【環球薈報】意內政部長親身拆毀犯罪集團豪宅","createTime":"2018-11-27T16:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T02:59:24.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e058fda98fdcbfda4531d0a17cb929e33013c5a1","tid":919034,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T16:58:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>【環球薈報】意內政部長親身拆毀犯罪集團豪宅</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】意大利家族式的有組織犯罪集團多年來被指影響廣大，從社會治安到金融和政界都有影響。意大利極右聯盟黨領袖薩爾維尼六月上任內政部長後，就雷厲風行打擊這股勢力。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報道，薩爾維尼身先士卒坐上挖土機，拆毀犯罪集團卡薩莫尼卡家族一間非法興建的豪宅，以示打擊罪案的決心。<br />\n<br />\n薩爾維尼坐上挖土機，為拆卸工程打響頭炮。這間豪宅相信是卡薩莫尼卡家族在多年前未經准許下違法興建，預料拆卸後會改建成兒童遊樂場。<br />\n<br />\n上星期六百名羅馬警方亦突擊另外八間卡薩莫尼卡家族的違法別墅，充公建築並拘捕了一些人。薩爾維尼指，政府會逐家逐戶、鍥而不捨地追捕犯罪分子。<br />\n<br />\n卡薩莫尼卡家族活躍於羅馬及市郊地區，涉足多個行業，包括建築、餐飲和販毒，估計擁有逾八億港元資產。<br />\n<br />\n2015年，前任家族首領的荷李活電影式葬禮用上豪華馬車，直升機在空中撒花，再配以電影《教父》主題曲，曾經哄動一時。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=328743&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D328743%26refer%3D&d=mfGtuK%2BokgppttSxVqbIfdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=bdf157e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D328743%26refer%3D&h=7a0c4adf\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=328743&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"dcdc6b93edc2f1f287dbd0aaf02859fd597949f9","tid":919034,"uid":125612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T17:31:28.000Z","msg":"harvey dent"},{"pid":"a10835aa43e08e95e5514506993e19532c1da898","tid":919034,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T23:55:52.000Z","msg":"好快俾人暗殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a1cfbf072fe40ed4d7604300e528bbb828e1e9","tid":919034,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcdc6b93edc2f1f287dbd0aaf02859fd597949f9","tid":919034,"uid":125612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T17:31:28.000Z","msg":"harvey dent"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:40:28.000Z","msg":"You either die a hero..."},{"pid":"e9e01e7170a339a075a444a2770337376746da66","tid":919034,"uid":91604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T02:59:24.000Z","msg":"講到咁勁都只係得8億港元資產<br />\n香港投共果個黑社會大佬,剩係隻殼都唔止呢個數"}]}